'BRUN BACK' TO ADD A NEW COMMAND TOPRODOS THAT SERVES AS THE EQUIVALENTTO 'CD ..' IN UNIX AND MS-DOSSYSTEMS.TYPE 'BACK' (OR EXECUTE 'JSR $0317'IN ASSEMBLY LANGUAGE) TO BACK UP THEPRODOSPREFIX ONE LEVEL.BE CAREFUL NOT TO 'BRUN BACK' AFTERIT HAS ALREADY BEEN INSTALLED; OR ITCOULD LOCK THE SYSTEM UP.